  "texts": [
    "b, We embedded the SAE and AAE texts in prompts that asked for properties of the speakers who uttered the texts.",
    "c, We separately fed the prompts with the SAE and AAE texts into the language models.",
    "d, We retrieved and compared the predictions for the SAE and AAE inputs, here illustrated by five adjectives from the Princeton Trilogy.",
    "See Methods for more details.",
    "the Princeton Trilogy [29] [30] [31] 34, a series of studies investigating the racial stereotypes held by Americans, with the difference that instead of overtly mentioning race to the language models, we used matched guise probing based on AAE and SAE texts (Methods)."
